{"id":120668,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：拥有共产朝鲜音乐在韩违法/","date":"2010-11-09T08:06:53Z","modified":"2010-11-09T08:06:53Z","title":"简讯：拥有共产朝鲜音乐在韩违法","content":"<div>\n<p>韩国最高法院作出裁决，拥有歌颂共产党北朝鲜的音乐是犯罪行为。</p>\n<p>法官决定维持先前对一名妇女作出的监禁缓刑判决，她被控以电子文件形式储存了北朝鲜歌颂领袖的音乐。</p>\n<p>最高法院表示，这些乐曲尽管没有歌词，但是包含“有利于敌人的表达”，对韩国安全构成威胁。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/fgHZ3oKeYFHtpdjNyMrhLeg2YJo/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/fgHZ3oKeYFHtpdjNyMrhLeg2YJo/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/fgHZ3oKeYFHtpdjNyMrhLeg2YJo/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/fgHZ3oKeYFHtpdjNyMrhLeg2YJo/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ywU2RlbSPQU:Jr8wQu9WNKM:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ywU2RlbSPQU:Jr8wQu9WNKM:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ywU2RlbSPQU:Jr8wQu9WNKM:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ywU2RlbSPQU:Jr8wQu9WNKM:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ywU2RlbSPQU:Jr8wQu9WNKM:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ywU2RlbSPQU:Jr8wQu9WNKM:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/ywU2RlbSPQU\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2010/11/101108_brief_korea_music.shtml\" title=\"简讯：拥有共产朝鲜音乐在韩违法\">简讯：拥有共产朝鲜音乐在韩违法</a></p>\n","author":138,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}